  "title": "Autocomplete search component",
  "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nI'm looking for a way to display suggestions on a search field, I saw that you have a autocomplete.js library but it looks outdated. I saw that there is a connectAutocomplete connector in instantsearch.js but the documentation about how to implement it is also outdated (404 links).\r\n\r\nDo you have any examples of a implementation of an angular 2+ / ssr / autocomplete search ?\r\n\r\nThanks !",
